  "remarks": "\nThe Secretary of State considers that there are reasonable grounds to suspect that\n SINARA BANK JOINT STOCK COMPANY has been, and is, obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely, the Russian financial services sector.  \n",
